{
  "chapter": 94,
  "chapter_summary": "第九十四回 机智绝伦\n\n苏樱被恶人谷四大恶人（白开心、哈哈儿、屠娇娇、李大嘴）围住，四人以帮助苏樱嫁给小鱼儿为条件，要求苏樱将小鱼儿带入魏无牙的洞府。苏樱以机智应对，甚至调侃李大嘴吃人肉的细节，让四大恶人反而心生疑虑。白开心对苏樱起色心，欲强行非礼，花无缺及时出现救下苏樱。四大恶人假装内讧趁机逃脱，留下讽刺字条。\n\n花无缺与苏樱展开对话，苏樱透露自己与铁心兰结拜为姊妹，并将铁心兰送到了魏无牙那里。花无缺因移花宫的规矩不得不杀苏樱灭口，但苏樱以仁义道德和铁心兰的情感要挟，最终让花无缺暂时放过她。花无缺赶往魏无牙处寻找铁心兰。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "苏姑娘，你用不着害怕，这两天我的胃口都不太好，要吃你，至少也得再等几天。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "像这样聪明标致的女孩儿，就算你舍得吃，我也不答应的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以我看来，还是吃了算了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "哈哈，你这人真是名副其实的损人不利己，李大嘴将她吃了，于你又有什么好处？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我至少可以放心些，不至于被她卖了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四位难道是来为铁心兰打抱不平的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "说起来，那傻丫头倒的确蛮可怜的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四位若是觉得我让她去上当，方才为何不拦住她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "她既不是我女儿，也不是我老婆，她上不上当，与我又有何关？我为何要来多事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况，让她到魏无牙那里去也不错，哈哈，魏无牙要是看中了她，那就简直更妙不可言了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，四位是为了什么来的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我们来找你，只不过是为了谈一项交易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "交易？什么交易？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "哈哈，自然是彼此有利的交易，却不知你肯不肯答应？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是彼此有利的交易，我怎么会不答应呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好，我问你，你想嫁给小鱼儿，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "我并不是想想就算了，我是非嫁他不可。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但你有把握让他娶你么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "越没有把握的事，做起来就越有趣，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好，现在我们可以帮你的忙，叫小鱼儿娶你，但你却也要答应我们一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们真有把握让他娶我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "当然有把握，你莫忘了，小鱼儿是我们养大的，我们怎会不知道他的脾气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "那么，你们又要我做什么事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "将他活着带入魏无牙的洞去，再活着带出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "你们为什么要这样做呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "只因为我们要叫他去拿件东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他若不肯去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他本来就算不一定会去，但现在却是非去不可的，只因为你帮了我们的忙，你将铁心兰送到那里去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是我不答应呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若不答应，我的胃口立刻就会变好的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信我身上的肉，无论怎么做，都很好吃的。只不过我要劝你，切切不要红烧，这么嫩的肉，红烧实在太可惜了，最好是用来涮锅子，肉才能保持鲜嫩。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倒提醒了我，涮人肉的滋味，的确可算是天下第一，我倒真的已有许久未曾尝过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你最好在我还活着的时候，就将我身上的肉片切下来，而且佐料中，切切不可放醋，因为人肉本来就有些酸的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多承指教，我吃人吃了无数，想不到竟还没有你内行。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你吃过这样的人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这丫头看起来，就像是喜欢被老子吃下去似的，真不知她肚子里在打什么鬼主意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你想，她若非胸有成竹，怎会如此笃定？而且还像是生怕死得太舒服了，竟劝你活着将她凌迟，你想，世上有这样的人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "text": "你的意思是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "依我之见，还是算了吧！咱们能活到现在，并不是件容易的事，莫要阴沟里翻船，栽在这小丫头手里，那才冤哩。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话倒也不错……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "你还不过来，再等下去，我的肉都要变老了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你的肉太酸，我懒得吃了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到我的肉竟是酸的，莫非是平时吃醋吃得太多了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和他不一样，他好吃，我好色。好吃的人，胆子总比较小些，但好色的人就不同了……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "常言道，色胆包天，这句话你总该听过的吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "阁下若觉得光棍做得无趣了，我倒可替你做个媒。那边小溪里，有位美人在沐浴，她不但长得千娇百媚，比我好看多了，而且风情万种，知情识趣。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我就看上了你，别的人我都不要。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男子汉，大丈夫，怎么能欺负女人！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花无缺！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有哪一位想动手的么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们也早就看这色鬼不顺眼，公子此刻教训了他，这是再好也没有。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜公子出手还太轻了些……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈，公子若将他抛得更远些，让咱们再也瞧不见才好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过想摸一摸她而已，但那大嘴巴却要吃她的肉哩！",
      "tone": "大叫",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位倒真是够义气得很……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "speaker_name": "白开心",
      "listener": "char_li_da_zui",
      "text": "大嘴狼，你敢打人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_zui",
      "speaker_name": "李大嘴",
      "listener": "char_bai_kai_xin",
      "text": "二十年前，我就想打死你这王八蛋了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ha_ha_er",
      "speaker_name": "哈哈儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，打得好，哈哈，快抓他的头发，对了，抓紧些。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不能让他们这样打下去，若是打死了一个，咱们岂非还得花钱为他收尸，还是过去拉开他们吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_jiao_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "屠娇娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要打了……再打就要打出人命来了呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花公子，你上了他们的当了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "上什么当？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你以为他们这真是在打架么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "难道这是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这不过是他们在想法子逃走而已。那俩人的武功虽然不怎么样，但若真的要拼命，三百招内，谁也休想碰着对方一根手指。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然上当，惭愧惭愧。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这四人的诡计多端，实在少见得很，像花公子这样的忠厚君子，若不上他们的当，那才是怪事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "忠厚君子，倒也未必未必……方才也有几个人就上了我的当。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "哦？谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不错，上当的必定就是白山君夫妇，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "正是他们。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我虽然以药力将你困住，但那药对人却没有什么害处的，只要一吹风药力就解了，只不过那时他们必已点了你穴道，你还是不能逃走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你是不是故意装成中毒很深的模样，让他们对你不加提防，你却在暗中以'移花接玉'的内力，打开了穴道，扬长而去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘的聪明智慧，实在也少见得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘你虽然是智计无双，但在下却知道还有一个人……就算姑娘你遇见他，只怕也要吃亏的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你说的不错，我非但知道你说的这人是谁，而且也吃过他的亏了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "温良如玉的花公子，如今也会以诡计骗人，只怕也就是跟这个人学的……我说的是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这就叫做：近朱者赤，近墨者黑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但君子毕竟总是君子，所以我虽然那么样对待你，你非但没有向我报复，反而救了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你可知道我为什么要救你？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我已说过，这就因为你是君子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我必须告诉你三件事，第一，移花接玉的秘密，绝不容许外人知道，谁知道了，只有死！这是移花宫的禁例，谁也不能例外。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "第二，移花宫的门下无论要做什么事，都必须自己动手，绝不容别人干涉，也绝不能假手于外人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "第……第三呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "第三，我也是移花宫的门下，无论如何，我也不能破坏移花宫的规矩。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "如此说来，你救了我，只不过是为了要亲手杀我而已，是么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "纵然情非得已，却也势在必行。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "那么……那么我也要告诉你三件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "第一，你莫要忘记，我本来有许多机会可以杀你的，但我却没有动手，你现在若杀了我，岂非不义？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "第二，我虽然知道了移花接玉的秘密，但我绝不会练这种功夫，也绝没有告诉过别人，你若杀了我，岂非不仁？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "第三，你莫忘了，我是个女人，而且手无缚鸡之力，一个大男人以强欺弱，来欺负一个弱女子，这非但无礼，简直是无耻了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你若一定要做这种不仁不义、无礼无耻的事，我自然也没法子，但铁心兰若是知道了，她一定会对你失望得很。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不错，铁心兰……她总是对我说，你是最温柔、最有礼的男人，我本来也很相信的，但现在……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你……你认识铁心兰？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我和她不算太亲密，只不过刚刚结拜为姊妹而已。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "不可能……这绝不可能！她在哪？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我就算告诉你她此刻在哪里，你也不敢去找她的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "魏无牙，你将她送到魏无牙那里去了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "魏无牙对别人虽凶恶，但对我们姊妹却很好的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "移花宫的秘密，你绝不告诉别人？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "若有第二个人知道，那时你再杀我也不迟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "那时虽已迟了，但……但我还是相信你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 94,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    }
